{"tid":567190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線：雲南女大學生入禀法院 追討父母'侵吞'5.8萬元利是錢","createTime":"2018-02-20T15:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T20:40:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b76e1f68362dab0f3a970e9440b733f0e7aea7","tid":567190,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"【你收到多少利是？】<br />\n【雲南女大學生入禀法院】<br />\n【追討5.8萬元利是錢】<br />\n<br />\n拜年逗利是，也是取其好意頭。有內地理財公司統計小朋友平均收到多少利是錢，香港小朋友大約收1000港幣。最多的是福建莆田的小朋友，平均收到12000元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n通常收到利是，小朋友也會上繳父母。有家長和女兒開玩笑，要「騙」走女兒的利是錢，但有家庭的確因為利是錢而對簿公堂，雲南一名女大學生便向法院追討父母以往「侵吞」她的5.8萬元<br />\n利是錢。<br />\n<br />\n在小朋友心中，利是的真正意義是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#利是錢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1644728732338273/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1644728732338273%2F&d=LG5iZRcf1akFTiRMjndvrS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2cdbaf7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1644728732338273/</a>"},{"pid":"80aa6cc81bf9ed9a6688d02ba21322c08a52b8a2","tid":567190,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"福建果D咁多既?"},{"pid":"63befed0a0c191ad6539c2bbc3f1e98198fad30d","tid":567190,"uid":40632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80aa6cc81bf9ed9a6688d02ba21322c08a52b8a2","tid":567190,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"福建果D咁多既?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"真係可以去到成皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申老母鄉下福建"},{"pid":"f246b56ad1fd863246bfec0ea5b10bcee7c756f5","tid":567190,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"大把本土人士上去逗利是"},{"pid":"0a2b8d422d9177d7b86fc19d5da41290167930c4","tid":567190,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63befed0a0c19